name: The Oranges Flat Notecard Set
description:
Set of 10 flat notecards, two of each design. Hand cut from mid-weight cardstock which features modern styles with a slightly weathered look. Plain white on the back.

The notecards measure 5" x 3.5" and included with the set are 10 white envelopes. Each set is nicely packaged with various styles of paper wrap tabs and placed in cellophane packaging.

Duplicate sets are available if needed.

Please let me know if you have any questions.

name: Deer Silhouette Print, Left Facing 5 x 7
description:
5 x 7 print with the silhouette of black deer facing to the left. The background is a colorful modern design with fuchsia, teal, and pink alongside tan and white.  It has a .25" white border.

With the original I used an image transfer process using transparency film and matte medium to create the background on watercolor paper. The deer was then painted on with black gouache.  

All prints are professionally scanned and printed on 100 lb. (heavy card stock) brilliant white paper at a local shop and they will be signed and shipped in a rigid mailer.  

*Color shades may vary slightly from monitor to monitor

name: Smoking Bear, 5 x7 Print
description:
5 x 7 print with the silhouette of black bear smoking a pipe. The background is a colorful modern design of bright yellow. The print has a .25" white border.

With the original I used an image transfer process using transparency film and fluid matte medium for the background on watercolor paper. It is an imperfect process which creates the uneven weathered look. The bear was then painted on with black gouache.

All prints are scanned and professionally printed on 100 lb. (thick card stock) brilliant white paper at a local shop and they will be signed and shipped in a rigid mailer.
